# EPICS TOC BEGIN
# Macros:
#  - BUS
#  - S
# Table of Contents DTYP INP OUT
# | Record                    | Value              | Type      | DTYP   | INP                                       | OUT                                       |
# | ------------------------- | ------------------ | --------- | ------ | ----------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
# | $(S):SET_CURR_SWEEP_LLIM4 |                    | ao        | ""     | NA                                        | ""                                        |
# | $(S):UPDATE               |                    | seq       | ""     | NA                                        | NA                                        |
